
Ivanhoe Server Installation Instructions (version 0.1, 2/2/07)
==========================================

1) Check out the ivanhoe java based client/server and the ivanweb ruby on rails application from svn. 
Place them in dirs: ivanhoe_deployment and ivanweb, respectively.

2) Modify the build.properties file for your system:

# Server Properties
server.hostname=localhost
server.game.port=4550
server.web.port=3000
server.mail.enabled=false
server.mail.hostname=l.mail.virginia.edu
server.newaccounts.allow=true

# Database Properties
db.host=localhost
db.name=ivanhoe_unstable
db.user=ivanhoe
db.pass=gam3

3) Run ant deploy-all

Starting the Server
=============================

1) Fire up the Ruby on Rails ivanweb application.

2) Go into the ivanweb/server directory and start the server:  java -jar ivanhoe-server.jar

